input.activity_signal: Web search results show Benjamin R. Humphreys Jr. as President/CEO of both Comtel Communications (founded 1991) and Simplicity VoIP, with active company website found at simplicityvoip.net. However, the FCC filing is from 2020-10-08 with no recent activity since then.
input.product_summary: Benjamin R. Humphreys Jr. operates Comtel Communications (a technology consulting agency) and Simplicity VoIP, providing voice and data services in the mid-Atlantic region.
